{"tid":2152542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★旺角現「藥房末日」　嬰兒奶粉賣50元　店員：清完就閃","createTime":"2020-08-12T04:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T12:41:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":359,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"475a195763b7dd67241c872250ae212dd18e125c","tid":2152542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"本港疫情持續，周末旺角街頭比昔日冷清，新的吉舖陸續湧現，西洋菜街及波鞋街分別有約12間及4間吉舖，部份吉舖的前身為時裝店、藥房及連銷藥妝店。有消息指，H&amp;M時裝旗下旺角家樂坊5萬呎旗艦店，月租達900萬元，亦將於約滿後不再續租。而多間店舖已貼上「租約期滿清貨減價」，有藥房在門外放置10、15、20元的特賣貨架，以低價售賣如保濟丸等藥物，更甚者，有原價約200元的奶粉大劈價至50元。而鞋店亦推出「買一送一」的優惠，甚至有散貨場將原價約600元的鞋款減至299元一對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/509480/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E7%8F%BE-%E8%97%A5%E6%88%BF%E6%9C%AB%E6%97%A5-%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%92%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E8%B3%A350%E5%85%83-%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1-%E6%B8%85%E5%AE%8C%E5%B0%B1%E9%96%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F509480%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%258F%25BE-%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%259C%25AB%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25AC%25B0%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E7%25B2%2589%25E8%25B3%25A350%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E9%2596%2583&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=e8ceac86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/509480/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E7%8F%BE-%E8%97%A5%E6%88%BF%E6%9C%AB%E6%97%A5-%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%92%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E8%B3%A350%E5%85%83-%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1-%E6%B8%85%E5%AE%8C%E5%B0%B1%E9%96%83</a>"},{"pid":"cb7e438189dd85056a0917db228e9cc5cf6b8fae","tid":2152542,"uid":19454,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.h